Package parser.seed.transducer.process

Class SeedTransducerConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.seed.transducer.process.SeedTransducerConverter
  • public abstract class SeedTransducerConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    Enables Seed Transducer's transformation from JSON to POJO. It is then transformed into a SeedTransducerParsingResult containing the SeedTransducer or errors.

    • Method Detail

      • convert

        public static SeedTransducerParsingResult convert​(java.io.File jsonFile)
        Transforms seed transducer JSON file into POJO before creating a SeedTransducerParsingResult. If a parsing error occurs the result will not contain ant SeedTransducer. Errors are added to the result. If the error is not a proper parsing error, processing errors can be notified.
        Parameters:
        jsonFile - - path to the seed transducer JSON file representation
        Returns:
        SeedTransducerParsingResult containing the SeedTransducer result or an empty Optional object and errors if the parsing did't go through

      • process

        private static SeedTransducerParsingResult process​(SeedTransducerPOJO pojo,
                                                   SeedTransducerParsingResult res)
        Process the parsing and converting.
        Parameters:
        pojo - The mapped SeedTransducerPOJO related to the Seed Transducer JSON file.
        res - The SeedTransducerParsingResult parsing result
        Returns:
        SeedTransducerParsingResult containing the SeedTransducer result or an empty Optional object and errors if the parsing did't go through
